==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Edulcorant
<hw>E*dul"co*rant</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Edulcorate</er>.]</ety> <def>Having a tendency to purify or to
sweeten by removing or correcting acidity and acrimony.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Edulcorant</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Edulcorant
<hw>E*dul"co*rant</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>An edulcorant
remedy.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Edulcorate</ent>⟦br⟧
